  "texts": [
    "The growing utilization of AI and ML in cybersecurity holds great potential for transforming the field; however, it also brings forth various challenges and obstacles to successful implementation.",
    "Among the frequently cited challenges, a significant hurdle is the lack of comprehension of the technology, as reported by 36.9% of surveyed organizations.",
    "This lack of understanding poses difficulties for organizations in adequately assessing and adopting AI and ML solutions.",
    "Moreover, it can impede their ability to effectively manage and monitor these systems.",
    "Another commonly encountered challenge is the scarcity of skilled personnel, which was reported by 34% of the surveyed organizations."
  ],
